	<div class="settings__section" id="irc">
		<h2>IRC</h2>
		<p>Set up the first IRC network that you want Pyramid to connect to. You can add another one later.</p>

		<div class="settings__section">
			<h2>Meta data</h2>

			<div class="network-type-selector">
				<div class="network-type-selector__head">
					<p>Select network type:</p>

					<ul class="settingsview__tabs switcher network-type-selector__switcher">
						<li><a class="<%= ircTypeClass %>" href="javascript://">Normal IRC</a></li>
						<li><a class="<%= twitchTypeClass %>" href="javascript://">Twitch</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<input type="hidden" class="network-type-selector__value" name="networkType" value="<%= reqBody.networkType || "irc" %>" />

				<div class="network-type-selector__main network-type-selector__irc" style="<%= ircTypeDisplay %>">
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircName">Network name </label>
						<input type="text" id="ircName" name="ircName"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircName || "" %>">  <em>(only for own identification; required)</em>
					</p>
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircHostname">Hostname </label>
						<input type="text" id="ircHostname" name="ircHostname"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircHostname || "" %>">  <em>(required)</em>
					</p>
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircPort">Port </label>
						<input type="number" id="ircPort" name="ircPort"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircPort || "6667" %>"> <em>(required)</em>
					</p>
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircNickname">Nickname </label>
						<input type="text" id="ircNickname" name="ircNickname"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircNickname || "" %>"> <em>(required)</em>
					</p>
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircUsername">Username </label>
						<input type="text" id="ircUsername" name="ircUsername"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircUsername || "" %>">
					</p>
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircPassword">Password </label>
						<input type="password" id="ircPassword" name="ircPassword"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircPassword || "" %>">
					</p>
					<p class="l">
						<label for="ircRealname">Real name </label>
						<input type="text" id="ircRealname" name="ircRealname"
							value="<%= reqBody.ircRealname || "" %>">
					</p>
					<p>
						<input type="checkbox" id="ircSecure" name="ircSecure"
							<%= reqBody.ircSecure ? " checked" : "" %>>
						<label for="ircSecure">Connect securely</label>
					</p>
					<p>
						<input type="checkbox" id="ircSelfSigned" name="ircSelfSigned"
